Biography

Nathan Carlin has had a successful career in track and field and cross country at Southern Utah University. Here's a breakdown of his performances in different events during the specified competitions:

2024 Outdoors:

Stanford Invitational

Took seventh in the 800m with a time of 1:55.90

UNLV Invite

Took sixth in the 400m with a time of 50.17 seconds.

SUU Coliseum Championships

Finished sixth in the 800m with a time of 1:54.13

BYU Robison Invitational

Finished the 400m with a time of 51.33 seconds

SUU Outdoor Championships

Took 11th in the 800m prelims with a time of 1:53.22

2024 Indoors:

BYU Cougar Invitational

Placed seventh in the 400m dash with a time of 50.93 seconds.

Lumberjack Team Challenge

Placed fifth in the 800m with a time of 1:55.33

UW Invitational

Placed third in the 800m with a time of 1:51.07

Finished the 1 mile with a time of 4:13.81

Husky Classic

Finished the 800m with a time of 1:58.82

WAC Championships

Placed seventh in the 800m with a time of 1:54.20

2023 XC:

UC Riverside: Nathan achieved a 25:04.8 in the 8k.

2023 Outdoors:

400 Meters: Nathan Carlin achieved a time of 52.10 seconds at the 2023 Utah Tech Invitational.

800 Meters: He completed the race in 1:52.70 at the 2023 WAC Outdoor Track & Field Championships, and he also participated in the 2023 Bryan Clay Invitational, finishing with times of 1:54.05 and 1:55.29.

1500 Meters: Nathan Carlin competed in the 2023 Bryan Clay Invitational, achieving a time of 3:55.70. He also participated in the 2023 Utah-WSU Spring Classic, completing the race in 4:07.75, and the Mike Fanelli Track Classic, where he finished in 4:00.94.

5000 Meters: At the 2023 WAC Outdoor Track & Field Championships, he achieved a time of 14:42.51 in the 5000 meters race.

4 x 400 Relay: No time was provided for the 4 x 400 Relay event at the 2023 Utah Tech Invitational.

2023 Indoors:

800 Meters: Nathan Carlin competed in the 2023 WAC Indoor Track and Field Championship, achieving times of 1:57.02 and 1:52.09.

Mile: He participated in the Ron Mann Classic and achieved a time of 4:27.96. Additionally, at the Lumberjack Team Challenge, he completed the mile in 4:32.24. In the 2023 BYU Cougar Indoor Invitational, he finished with a time of 4:38.63.

3000 Meters: At the 2023 WAC Indoor Track and Field Championship, he achieved a time of 8:45.66. He also participated in the Ron Mann Classic, completing the race in 9:17.96.

Distance Medley Relay: Nathan Carlin competed in the 2023 WAC Indoor Track and Field Championship, where his team achieved a time of 10:08.68.

2022 XC:

8k: He participated in the 2022 WAC Conference XC Meet, completing the race in 24:38.2. He also competed in the Weis-Crockett Invitational and finished with a time of 25:10.7. In the UCR 41st Annual Cross Country Invitational, he achieved a time of 25:16.5.

10k: At the NCAA Division I Mountain Region Cross Country Championships, Nathan Carlin completed the 10k race in 30:36.3.

5 Mile: He participated in the Joe Piane Invitational and achieved a time of 25:01.3.

Overall, Nathan Carlin has showcased his skills as a middle-distance and long-distance runner, competing in various events such as the 400 meters, 800 meters, 1500 meters, 5000 meters, mile, 3000 meters, and cross country races. His performances demonstrate a consistent level of competence and involvement in both indoor and outdoor track and field events as well as cross country at Southern Utah University.
